false"\nUnhideWhenUsed="false" QFormat="true" Name="Intense Emphasis" />\n<w:LsdException Locked="false" Priority="31" SemiHidden="false"\nUnhideWhenUsed="false" QFormat="true" Name="Subtle Reference" />\n<w:LsdException Locked="false" Priority="32" SemiHidden="false"\nUnhideWhenUsed="false" QFormat="true" Name="Intense Reference" />\n<w:LsdException Locked="false" Priority="33" SemiHidden="false"\nUnhideWhenUsed="false" QFormat="true" Name="Book Title" />\n<w:LsdException Locked="false" Priority="37" Name="Bibliography" />\n<w:LsdException Locked="false" Priority="39" QFormat="true" Name="TOC Heading" />\n</w:LatentStyles>\n</xml><![endif]--><!--[if gte mso 10]>\n<style>\n/* Style Definitions */\ntable.MsoNormalTable\n{mso-style-name:"Table Normal";\nmso-tstyle-rowband-size:0;\nmso-tstyle-colband-size:0;\nmso-style-noshow:yes;\nmso-style-priority:99;\nmso-style-qformat:yes;\nmso-style-parent:"";\nmso-padding-alt:0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt;\nmso-para-margin:0in;\nmso-para-margin-bottom:.0001pt;\nmso-pagination:widow-orphan;\nfont-size:11.0pt;\nfont-family:"Cambria","serif";\nmso-ascii-font-family:Cambria;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Cambria;\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;}\n</style>\n<![endif]-->\n<p class="MsoNormal">Firebird Speed is a speed-funding service for start-up businesses and projects in Russia, the C.I.S. to use to quickly find interested investors in the US and Western Europe of various sizes and capabilities, as well as through crowdsourcing.<span style="mso-spacerun:yes">&nbsp; </span>We aim to help, in a personalized, comfortable fashion to help investors meet with multiple technology and new media businesses/projects sorted by area of specialty, investment requirements, and other factors specific to the needs of both businesses and investors.<span style="mso-spacerun:yes">&nbsp; </span>The concept is to allow extremely unique, first-hand access without wasting your time or worrying about security, confidentiality, and the ability to perform needed due diligence.</p>\n<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;Before members are registered to be able to participate, they must submit enough information so as Firebird itself can perform its own diligence before giving access to its systems.<span style="mso-spacerun:yes">&nbsp; </span>This is done via the intake membership applications we require.<span style="mso-spacerun:yes">&nbsp; </span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;Once companies and projects are approved, many will be showcased in our general portfolio, especially those marked as &ldquo;hot&rdquo; by ourself and participating analysts from the world&rsquo;s top investment institutions.<span style="mso-spacerun:yes">&nbsp; </span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;Investors will be allowed to reveal as much or as little information about themselves publicly if you request it to be confidential.<span style="mso-spacerun:yes">&nbsp; </span>NDA contracts are signed electronically with Firebird in the registration process.<span style="mso-spacerun:yes">&nbsp; </span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;Investors and companies/projects will be allowed to register for and participate in hour long speed-funding sessions, both general, and specified by type of business/project and investor requirements and preferences.<span style="mso-spacerun:yes">&nbsp; </span>They will be given, during these sessions, 5 minutes to communicate with one another before being switched to other relevant investors and companies/projects, in between which both parties will be able to indicate their opinions on one another.<span style="mso-spacerun:yes">&nbsp; </span>Communications take place via audio with integrated IM capability instant-translation capabilities are available.</p>\n<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;Following the sessions, both investors and companies/project managers will receive a follow-up report listing companies and projects they have rated as attractive.<span style="mso-spacerun:yes">&nbsp; </span>They will then have the ability to, through our private conferencing rooms, schedule lengthier one-on-one sessions, and more documentation on the companies will be made available as requested.<span style="mso-spacerun:yes">&nbsp; </span>Firebird will assist investors obtain the necessary due diligence and companies formulate the proper financials and other documentation in the format needed by investors in this process, as part of the initial, minimal registration fee.</p>\n<p class="MsoNormal">Once an investor is ready to move forward, if the company/project is in agreement, they will be asked to signed an electronic NDA and LOI with each other as well as place monies in escrow through secured software provided by Firebird, as well as signing an additional document regarding the terms of the escrow funds.<span style="mso-spacerun:yes">&nbsp; </span>Firebird will guarantee that, once monies are placed in escrow, it will perform all additional diligence needed, disclose full details on both parties to one another, and assist in preparing the legal documentation needed to secure investment.<span style="mso-spacerun:yes">&nbsp; </span>Off-line Firebird legal consultants will participate, as needed, in this process.<span style="mso-spacerun:yes">&nbsp; </span>Once monies are placed in escrow, the investor will have 2 weeks-month, according to the company/project&rsquo;s request maximum, on an exclusive basis, to either complete the investment or not.<span style="mso-spacerun:yes">&nbsp; </span>Ten percent of the monies will regardless of the decision be retained by Firebird in exchange for its services.<span style="mso-spacerun:yes">&nbsp; </span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal">Our goal is to provide maximum comfort for all parties with minimal risk.<span style="mso-spacerun:yes">&nbsp; </span>We aim to garner and facilitate investments, without having to leave the comfort of your home/office, as quickly as possible, and in no more than two months, generally, depending on the size of the investment needed.<span style="mso-spacerun:yes">&nbsp; </span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal">We also allow investors to be placed in contact with like-minded investors, if they request, who share interest in certain companies/projects so as to allow them to partner as desired.</p>\n<p class="MsoNormal">Finally, we offer certain crowdsourcing services for interested companies and projects.<span style="mso-spacerun:yes">&nbsp; </span>However, companies who request crowdsourcing options, will not be allowed to participate in speed-funding sessions with investors requesting exclusivity or considering sizable investments.<span style="mso-spacerun:yes">&nbsp; </span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal">All investors will be given access to speed-funding and follow-up services, crowdsourcing options, and a plethora of additional more specified pay services, whereby Firebird will offer rights of first access and first refusal to specified projects and also seek out actively projects and companies that may not be readily accessible via the site.</p>\n<p class="MsoNormal">The site is also open to existing incubators, accelerators and venture capital funds seeking additional investment for specific projects or in general.<span style="mso-spacerun:yes">&nbsp; </span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal">So, sit back, relax, and get the most unique access to the broadest range of companies, projects, and investors you otherwise would likely never have known about, with the knowledge that, should you find your ideal partner, Firebird will help you court and seal the deal with extremely minimal expense and little to no risk.<span style="mso-spacerun:yes">&nbsp; </span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal">So, what are you waiting for?<span style="mso-spacerun:yes">&nbsp; </span>Start growing your ideas, your companies, and your portfolios right now.<span style="mso-spacerun:yes">&nbsp; </span></p>\n</p>', 0, 1);
